import React, { Component, lazy, Suspense } from 'react'; import { Bar, Line } from 'react-chartjs-2'; import { Badge, Button, ButtonDropdown, ButtonGroup, ButtonToolbar, Card, CardBody, CardFooter, CardHeader, CardTitle, Col, Dropdown, DropdownItem, DropdownMenu, DropdownToggle, Progress, Row, Table } from 'reactstrap'; import { getStyle, hexToRgba } from '@coreui/coreui/dist/js/coreui-utilities'; import track from 'react-tracking'; import API from '../../../utils/API'; import { cardChartData1, cardChartOpts1, cardChartData2, cardChartOpts2, cardChartData3, cardChartOpts3, cardChartData4, cardChartOpts4, makeSocialBoxData, socialChartOpts, makeSparkLineData, sparklineChartOpts, mainChartOpts } from './data' import './Dashboard.css'; const Widget03 = lazy(() => import('../../../components/Widgets/Widget03')); const brandPrimary = getStyle('--primary') const brandSuccess = getStyle('--success') const brandInfo = getStyle('--info') const brandWarning = getStyle('--warning') const brandDanger = getStyle('--danger') class Dashboard extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.toggle = this.toggle.bind(this); this.onRadioBtnClick = this.onRadioBtnClick.bind(this); this.state = { dropdownOpen: false, radioSelected: 2, traffic:[], error:false, mainChart:{} }; } componentDidMount () { var week_lag = new Date(); var weekInMilliseconds = 7 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000; var weekNum=2; week_lag.setTime(week_lag.getTime() - weekNum * weekInMilliseconds); API.get_event({ page:'Chat', created_at : {"$gte": week_lag} },{ created_at: 1 }).then((data) => { let traffic=data.data.data; console.log(traffic.length) if(traffic.length>0){ let date_min=new Date(traffic[0].created_at); let date_max=new Date(traffic[traffic.length-1].created_at); console.log(date_min,date_max); var elements = 27; var date_array = []; var traffic_data = []; for (var i = 1; i <= elements; i++) { var intermDate = new Date(date_min.getTime() + i * (date_max.getTime() - date_min.getTime()) / elements ); console.log(intermDate) date_array.push(intermDate); var date_low = new Date(date_array[i-1].getTime()); var date_high = new Date(date_array[i].getTime()); let trafficInWindow = traffic.filter(l => { return l.created_at.isAfter(date_low) && l.created_at.isBefore(date_high); }); console.log(trafficInWindow) traffic_data.push(intermDate); } console.log(date_array); console.log(traffic_data); const updatedTraffic = traffic.map(event => { return 100 }); console.log(updatedTraffic) this.setState({ traffic: updatedTraffic, mainChart: { labels: ['Mo', 'Tu', 'We', 'Th', 'Fr', 'Sa', 'Su', 'Mo', 'Tu', 'We', 'Th', 'Fr', 'Sa', 'Su', 'Mo', 'Tu', 'We', 'Th', 'Fr', 'Sa', 'Su', 'Mo', 'Tu', 'We', 'Th', 'Fr', 'Sa', 'Su'], datasets: [ { label: 'My First dataset', backgroundColor: hexToRgba(brandInfo, 10), borderColor: brandInfo, pointHoverBackgroundColor: '#fff', borderWidth: 2, data: updatedTraffic, } ], } }); console.log(data.data.data) } }, (error) => { this.setState({error: true}); console.log(error); return; }) } toggle() { this.setState({ dropdownOpen: !this.state.dropdownOpen, }); } onRadioBtnClick(radioSelected) { this.setState({ radioSelected: radioSelected, }); } loading = () =>
